thread.title_full: Mabel's Labels reviewed by eu tom

author: eu tom
title: eu tom
text: These labels seem pricey, but they're totally worth it because they're durable and waterproof. They came exactly like the proof shown on my computer screen. I like that they have an option of multi-color background or even the solid background which allows me to choose color. Great product! I would definitely recommend.
